    energy rise in the outflow from E ∼ 1046 to E ∼ 1049 erg with
    outflow speed β ≈ 0.05, while the off-axis relativistic jet solution
    instead suggests E ≈ 1052 erg with Lorentz factor Γ ∼ 10 at late
